metadata.name: Funeral For Foundation Collection 1/1
metadata.description:
Funeral For Foundation Collection 1/1
Rest In (Master) Pieces Collection

The purpose of this NFT is to commemorate the Foundation smart contract and all the other NFTs minted on the Foundation Collection of 2021-2022 This NFT was intended to be the the last, if not one of the last, NFTs minted to the Foundation Collection smart contract. To bid farewell and pay respects. January 28th, 2022

Image Description: 
Hi-res scan of authentic photograph of an unknown burial.
Original Photography and Development occurred in September 1957
After digitization, the original photograph was destroyed by fire.

Artist: Pitt Ripply
Theme: Vintage
Title: Funeral For Foundation Collection (Rest In Masterpieces)
Resolution: 600p
Dimension : 4000 x 4000p
Size: 20.1MB
